50|$|Young-min {{walked home}} {{as he thought}} to himself. It snowed when he reached home. Upon {{reaching}} home, he found Hee-dong and Hong-guan waiting for him, {{waiting for him to}} join the feast. Hee-dong poured the wine. As they knocked their first glass to drink their first toast, Hongguan drank for <b>the</b> <b>friendship</b> <b>bond</b> between <b>the</b> themselves.|$|R
